June 12 2023 
The day #two became #one 💍 

@future_jonez  and I had an #intimate #private #elopmentwedding  at our favourite park, overlooking the city . 

When you meet your person , how or when you decide to make them a part of your life forever , is no ones decision to make but your own . I knew from the #first #kiss that he was also going to be my last . 👑 

Having that person that just “gets you “ with no #hesitation, #questions or #judgments it’s legit a blessing from god . 

Never did either of us not be 100% ourselves . #vunerable #open and #transparent from day 1 with each other . Similar ideals , morals , goals and dreams . That with the right person we knew we could achieve . 

This time last year was the saddest and now will be the happiest time of my life , and again all part of the bigger plan .

We have both learned all the lessons #god needed us to , and finally lead each of us to one another . 
From #friends to #lovers  and then #partners to grow and build together . 
We thank you all for the support and look forward to sharing our love adventure with you. 
This song will forever always be special - but never as special as when @future_jonez  sings it to me . 
I love you baby 
goat and bunny forever
